member.name: F:Microsoft.Azure.Ipam.Contracts.IpamQueryPolicies.FirstSubtreeOnly
member.summary: Stop search next subtree after find enough result. For example, If there are following 2 avaliable space : space 1.2.0.0/23 under allocation 1.2.0.0/16, and space 1.3.0.0/24 space under allocation 1.3.0.0/24 Then when use this flag for a /24 space, after query find 1.2.0.0/24 under first allocation, query will stop continue search space. the result will be 1.2.0.0/24. And when not use this flag for a /24 space,after query find 1.2.0.0/24 under first allocation, query will continue search space and find 1.3.0.0/24. the result will be 1.2.0.0/24 or 1.3.0.0/24.

member.name: F:Microsoft.Azure.Ipam.Contracts.IpamQueryPolicies.WithAttributes
member.summary: WithAttributes means return the allocation along with the attributes information.

member.name: F:Microsoft.Azure.Ipam.Contracts.IpamQueryPolicies.BigSpaceFirst
member.summary: Use big space first in result. For example, If there are following 2 avaliable space : space 1.2.0.0/23 under allocation 1.2.0.0/16, and space 1.3.0.0/24 space under allocation 1.3.0.0/24 Then when use this flag for a /24 space, the result space will be 1.2.0.0/24 And when not use this flag for a /24 space, the result space will be 1.3.0.0/24
